==Demographics==
{| class="wikitable" style="float:right; margin-left:3px; text-size:80%; text-align:right"
|align=center colspan=2| '''City of Tel Aviv<br>Population by year'''<ref name="profile" /><ref name="Economist" /><ref name="population" /><ref name="UNESCO" /><ref name="JewishVL" />
|-
|1920 || 2,000
